This project includes software and design documentation for
software-driven networking on SONiC, including:

  - newtron: Network automation system for SONiC devices
  - newtrun: End-to-end test orchestration framework
  - newtlab: Virtual network lab orchestration (QEMU/KVM)
  - Design principles for open network automation

Project home: https://github.com/aldrin-isaac/newtron
